        "time_created": "2025-02-12T21:49:39.939Z",
        "time_updated": "2025-04-23T20:49:17.745Z",
        "edit_count": 3,
        "description": "<p>Artwork created for the Infinito Festival.</p><p>KIAM about this artwork: \"There are symbologies with profound meanings within a given historical and cultural context, and when embraced by society as a whole, they awaken a feeling of belonging and unity. In this piece we have the representation of an anonymous face that literally wears the symbols of its community, symbologies that carry some duality in their meaning, this duplicity being an aspect that seals such a unique identity into the DNA of the Torre neighbourhood. Behind a posture that distrusts with its gaze, collecting its hands, sprout abstract colours and desires that are sometimes camouflaged in this duality of symbolism\".</p>",
        "artists_count": 2,
        "artist1_title": "Gonçalo MAR",
        "artist1_url": "https://streetartcities.com/artists/gonalomar",
