        "title": "ontem, hoje e amanhã ",
        "description": "<p>The mural painted by Jorge Charrua symbolizes the historical celebration of the 25th of April, while also acts as a reminder that freedom is a constant struggle.</p><p>This piece is part of The Circuit of Valença, organized by FOmE and the Municipality of Valença. </p>",
