        "description": "<p>Jorge Charrua is one of the artists of MurArcos 2025. His work stands out for the presence of the human figure within a world of urban symbols and iconography, blending memory, empowerment, and references from art history.<br><br>MurArcos is an Urban Art Festival in Arcos de Valdevez organised by Regg Salgado, Mariana Duarte Santos and Daniela Guerreiro.</p>",
