        "title": "Cheta",
        "description": "<div><!--block-->This work by the artists Draw &amp; Contra honours a typical character from the city of Águeda, Zé Cheta. Although there is not much information about this person, who earned pennies by running errands and delivering parcels, we can say that the affection of the people of Águeda was felt from the first moment. A true example of empathy and (possible) diversity to be promoted in communities.</div>",
